  <p class="lead">The GRO’s Indexes of Birth, Marriages and Deaths provides a summary of the&#160; information in their registers, but they <strong>do not</strong> list everything that you would expect to find on a cetificate. Here you will find a description of the GRO Index pages and how might search FreeBMD.</p>

