  <h2 id="notGiven"> Information not given in the Indexes</h2>
  <p>As has been explained, the GRO Indexes contains only a summary of the information held by the GRO. To get more information you will need to purchase the certificate (or, more accurately, a certified copy of an entry in the register). You can find out however to do this, and what the certificate contains, from our [Ordering Certificates page] [link="Ordering Certificates"].</p>

